# ::snt I saw 765 astronauts, 122 museums, 13 diamonds and 235 lions.

   :ARG0 (i / i)
   :ARG1 (r / and
            :op1 (a / astronaut
                    :quant 765)
            :op2 (m / museum
                    :quant 122)
            :op3 (d / diamond
                    :quant 13)
            :op4 (l / lion
                    :quant 235)))

# ::suppl long_lists_1

        :ARG0 (i / i)
        :ARG1 (r / and
                 :op1 (c / cat
                         :quant 376)
                 :op2 (b / barrel
                         :quant 3874)
                 :op3 (v / veterinarian

                 :op5 (d / diamond

        :ARG0 (i / i)
        :ARG1 (u_1648 / and
                      :op1 (d / dog
                              :quant 376)
                      :op2 (r / rat
                              :quant 15)

                              :quant 51)

# ::snt Please buy chips, a knife, beer and expensive food.
# ::tree template(coord_4(chips,knife,beer,expensive_food))
# ::id long_lists_32
# ::suppl long_lists_32
(v / buy-01
   :mode imperative
   :polite +
   :ARG0 (y / you)
   :ARG1 (r / and
            :op1 (c / chip)
            :op2 (k / knife)
            :op3 (b / beer)
            :op4 (f / food
                    :mod (e / expensive))))

# ::id she_visited_countries_sanity_check_38
# ::suppl she_visited_countries_sanity_check_38
(v / visit-01
   :ARG0 (s / she)
   :ARG1 (c / country
            :wiki "Singapore"
            :name (n / name
                     :op1 "Singapore")))
